Third-party bundled assets
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Twemoji (assets/twemoji/*.svg)
------------------------------
The emoji graphics bundled under `assets/twemoji/` are from the Twemoji
project and are used as the default, platform-uniform emoji glyph set.

  Copyright 2020 Twitter, Inc and other contributors
  Graphics licensed under CC-BY 4.0:
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
  Source: https://github.com/jdecked/twemoji

CC-BY 4.0 requires attribution. This NOTICE, together with the credit in the
README, provides that attribution. If you swap the default `EmojiRenderer`
away from Twemoji (e.g. to native OS glyphs via `defaultEmojiRenderer`, or to
your own uniform set), the Twemoji attribution requirement no longer applies
to your build.

Starter stickers (assets/stickers/*.svg, assets/stickers/*.json)
----------------------------------------------------------------
Original works created for refraction_ui, licensed under the package's MIT
License. These are a small starter pack; hosts supply their own via the
`RefractionEmojiPicker.stickers` seam.
